platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Screen-searing graphics, great controls, white-knuckle action—Shadow Blade: Reload boasts all the ingredients for ninja-game magic. Its side-scrolling gameplay deftly blends wall-jumping acrobatics and sword-swinging combat, while motion-comic interludes lay out a sizzling story. And once you’ve mastered the campaign, you can prove your skills in a challenge mode aimed at the fiercest of warriors.
